lead_paragraph: Hur Mi-jung reeled off five consecutive birdies on her way to a one-shot lead after the first round at the Texas Shootout in Irving on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Hur Takes First-Round LPGA Lead as Wie Struggles Again
